Package com.ocr.jeanlouis34.escapegame.player

Class PlayerJoueur

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ocr.jeanlouis34.escapegame.player.PlayerJoueur
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Player
    public class PlayerJoueur
extends java.lang.Object
implements Player
    This class is the twin class of Player Machine. This class is only linked with the JeuDefenseur Class in the Defenseur pattern. This class enables to compare both automatically and handly made combinaisons. That is why it uses the variables of all the classes about COMBINAISON. WARNING : I have introduced a overrated level which enables to detect if the Human Player have cheated.
